## Sysadmin Mental Models

| Git Concept | Your Sysadmin Equivalent |
|---|---|
| Repository | A project folder with full backup history |
| Commit | System snapshot / restore point |
| Branch | Sandbox VM — test without touching production |
| Merge | Promoting sandbox changes to production |
| Push / Pull | Syncing to/from a central server |
| Stash | Pausing a task — save state, switch context |
| `.gitignore` | Files you'd never back up (logs, temp files) |
| Revert | Rolling back a bad patch safely |
| Reset --hard | Wiping a VM to last good snapshot ⚠️ |

